  "title": "Table - Top Cleaners needed at Hawker",
  "description": "<p><strong>PRIMARY RESPONSIBILITIES </strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Table cleaning/arranging dining chairs in an orderly manner.</p>\n<p>2. Wiping of Tables, Chairs, Food Trays.</p>\n<p>3. Spot/mop clean flooring/dining areas.</p>\n<p>4. Clearing of refuses from waste receptacles to bin centre and replace all bin liners. </p>\n<p>5. Cleaning of spills, broken glassware whenever required </p>\n<p>6. Report of any sanitation or janitorial issues to Immediate Superior.</p>\n<p>7. Adhere to safety regulations as stipulated by the Company.</p>\n<p>8. Perform duties as assigned by supervisor. </p>",
